# GuidedUp — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in values as needed.
#
# Currently no external services are used.
# All features run locally with in-memory storage.
#
# Future (post-alpha) variables:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...     # for AI-generated agendas
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_...            # for email reminders
# SUPABASE_URL=https://...         # for persistent PostgreSQL
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=ey...          # for auth + database access
